# Frontend Admin Router -> API Map

Mục tiêu:
- Bản rút gọn để team frontend code nhanh khu vực `ADMIN`.
- Chỉ tập trung vào: route nào gọi API nào, action nào dùng endpoint nào.

Phạm vi:
- Áp dụng cho `UserRole.ADMIN`.

---

## 1) Router map tổng quát

| Router | API load chính | API action chính |
|-------|-----------------|------------------|
| `/admin` | Chưa có API dashboard tổng hợp riêng. Có thể load nhanh từ `GET /admin/users`, `GET /admin/workspaces`, `GET /admin/audit-logs?limit=10`. | Không có |
| `/admin/users` | `GET /admin/users` | `PATCH /admin/users/:userId/lock` |
| `/admin/workspaces` | `GET /admin/workspaces` | `PATCH /admin/workspaces/:workspaceId/disable` |
| `/admin/audit-logs` | `GET /admin/audit-logs?workspaceId=&action=&limit=` | Không có |
| `/admin/quick-chat/agents` | `GET /admin/quick-chat/agents` | Điều hướng sang edit |
| `/admin/quick-chat/agents/:agentId` | Có thể load từ `GET /admin/quick-chat/agents` rồi find theo `agentId` ở FE | `PUT /admin/quick-chat/agents/:agentId` |
| `/admin/quick-chat/tools` | `GET /admin/quick-chat/tools` | Không có |
| `/admin/dev/payment-webhook` | Không cần load | `POST /topups/webhook` |
| `/admin/internal-quick-chat` | `POST /internal/quick-chat/sessions` -> `GET /internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId` | `POST /internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId/messages`, `POST /internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId/actions/:actionId/confirm` |

---

## 2) `/admin/users`

### Load
- `GET /admin/users`

### Fields nên render
- `id`
- `email`
- `fullName`
- `role`
- `status`
- `createdAt`

### Row actions
- Lock user:
  - `PATCH /admin/users/:userId/lock`
  - body:
```json
{ "locked": true }
```
- Unlock user:
  - `PATCH /admin/users/:userId/lock`
  - body:
```json
{ "locked": false }
```

---

## 3) `/admin/workspaces`

### Load
- `GET /admin/workspaces`

### Fields nên render
- `id`
- `name`
- `slug`
- `ownerUserId`
- `status`
- `createdAt`

### Row actions
- Disable workspace:
  - `PATCH /admin/workspaces/:workspaceId/disable`

---

## 4) `/admin/audit-logs`

### Load
- `GET /admin/audit-logs`

### Query gợi ý
- `workspaceId`
- `action`
- `limit`

### Fields nên render
- `createdAt`
- `actorUserId`
- `workspaceId`
- `action`
- `resourceType`
- `resourceId`
- `metadataJson`

---

## 5) `/admin/quick-chat/agents`

### Load
- `GET /admin/quick-chat/agents`

### Fields nên render
- `id`
- `name`
- `provider`
- `systemPrompt`
- `allowedTools`
- `skills`
- `active`
- `createdAt`
- `updatedAt`

---

## 6) `/admin/quick-chat/agents/:agentId`

### Save
- `PUT /admin/quick-chat/agents/:agentId`

### Body
```json
{
  "name": "John",
  "provider": "openai",
  "systemPrompt": "You are a workspace operations assistant.",
  "allowedTools": ["*"],
  "skills": ["workspace-ops", "billing-safety"],
  "active": true
}
```

---

## 7) `/admin/quick-chat/tools`

### Load
- `GET /admin/quick-chat/tools`

### Render
- Danh sách string tool name
- copy-to-clipboard

---

## 8) `/admin/dev/payment-webhook`

### Action
- `POST /topups/webhook`

### Body mẫu success
```json
{
  "provider": "mock_gateway",
  "eventId": "EVT_1",
  "topupCode": "TP_123",
  "status": "success",
  "amountInclVat": 110000
}
```

### Body mẫu failed
```json
{
  "provider": "mock_gateway",
  "eventId": "EVT_2",
  "topupCode": "TP_123",
  "status": "failed"
}
```

---

## 9) `/admin/internal-quick-chat`

### Tạo session
- `POST /internal/quick-chat/sessions`

### Body
```json
{
  "workspaceId": "WS_ID",
  "title": "Admin ops"
}
```

### Lấy session
- `GET /internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId`

### Gửi message
- `POST /internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId/messages`

### Confirm action
- `POST /internal/quick-chat/sessions/:sessionId/actions/:actionId/confirm`

---

## 10) Gợi ý code frontend

- `/admin` nên là hub nhẹ, không cần phụ thuộc API dashboard riêng.
- `/admin/quick-chat/agents/:agentId` có thể reuse data từ list để giảm thêm 1 request.
- Với webhook dev page, nhớ cảnh báo rõ đây là tool nội bộ/demo.
